
%hmtl
  %head
    %link{href:'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:200,300,400', rel:'stylesheet'}
  %body{style: "background: #272935; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; text-align: center;"}
    = image_tag 'logo_light.png', style: 'height: 100px; margin: 50px 0;'
    %div{style: 'background: #fff; width: 60vw; border-radius: 4px; padding: 40px; text-align: left; font-weight: 300;'}
      %h1
        Bonjour #{@resource.username},
      %p
        Il semblerait que tu aies demandé à changer ton mot de passe. Tu peux le faire en cliquant sur le bouton ci-dessous. Si cette demande n’est pas tienne, ignore cet e-mail.
      = render partial: 'shared/mailers/link_button', locals: {link: edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), text: 'Changer mon mot de passe'}
    %footer{style: 'margin: 50px; color: #fff; opacity: 0.3;'}
      = image_tag "#{root_url}images/emails/icon.png", style: 'height: 40px'
      %p
        Retrouvez-nous sur:
      %div{style: 'display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; justify-content: center;'}
        = link_to 'https://www.facebook.com/letsdevatig2i/' do
          = image_tag "#{root_url}images/emails/facebook.png", style: 'height: 30px; margin: 0 10px;'
        = link_to 'https://twitter.com/LetsDevAtIG2I' do
          = image_tag "#{root_url}images/emails/twitter.png", style: 'height: 30px; margin: 0 10px;'
      %p
        = link_to URI.parse(root_url).host, root_url, style: 'color: #fff;'
